IF there's anything footballers enjoy just as much as playing the beautiful game, it has to be dressing up. It's not often that supporters catch a glimpse of their favourite players wearing anything other than their soccer gear. But when footballers share their off the pitch lifestyle with supporters through social media, they usually make sure they impress. If it's not the flashy cars and jewelry, it's their unique taste of fashion which sets them apart from most people. Here, we take a look at some of the best dressers in the PSL, in no particular order. Lehlohonolo Majoro Keagan Buchanan Thembinkosi Lorch  Siphiwe Tshabalala Dumisani Zuma 